description:
TermPointToMme:  Records of MME (Mobility Management Entity) parameters for each cell, including IP addresses, supported RATs (Radio Access Technologies), and operational status.

- dateTime: Timestamp of the record.
- Area_Name: Name of the geographic area.
- CellId: Unique identifier of the cell site.
- Id2: Redundant CellId.
- Id3:  MME identifier (likely a composite key).
- vsDataType:  Data type identifier.
- vsDataFormatVersion: Version of the data format.
- TermPointToMme.mmeSupportNbIoT: Boolean indicating NB-IoT support.
- TermPointToMme.usedIpAddress: Currently used IP address of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.ipAddress1: Primary IP address of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.ipAddress2: Secondary IP address of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.servedPlmnListOtherRATs: List of PLMNs served by other RATs.
- TermPointToMme.mmeCodeListOtherRATs: List of MME codes for other RATs.
- TermPointToMme.relativeMmeCapacity: Relative capacity of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.mmeName: Name of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.additionalCnRef: Additional connection reference.
- TermPointToMme.ipv6Address1: Primary IPv6 address of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.mmeCodeListLTERelated: List of MME codes for LTE-related functions.
- TermPointToMme.ipv6Address2: Secondary IPv6 address of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.mmeSupportLegacyLte: Boolean indicating legacy LTE support.
- TermPointToMme.mmeGIListLTERelated: List of Global Identifiers (GIs) for LTE-related functions.
- TermPointToMme.servedPlmnListLTERelated: List of PLMNs served by LTE-related functions.
- TermPointToMme.administrativeState: Administrative state of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.domainName: Domain name of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.termPointToMmeId: Unique identifier of the MME-Cell association.
- TermPointToMme.availabilityStatus: Availability status of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.operationalState: Operational state of the MME.
- TermPointToMme.dcnType: Type of Data Communication Network (DCN).
